Package edu.ncsu.csc216.turn_taker.model.util

Interface SwapQueue<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - queue element
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SwapLinkedQueue

    public interface SwapQueue<E>
    Maintains a queue of element. Elements are added to the end of the queue and removed from the front of the queue. This queue provides the functionality for swapping neighboring elements.
    Author:
    Sarah Heckman
